ull, \"first\", String.class)).containsExactly(\"first\");\n\n        String[] values = {\"first\", \"second\"};\n        assertThat(LazyList.addToArray(values, \"third\", null)).containsExactly(\"first\", \"second\", \"third\");\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void removesItemFromTypedArray() {\n        String[] values = {\"first\", \"second\", \"third\"};\n\n        assertThat(LazyList.removeFromArray(values, \"second\")).containsExactly(\"first\", \"third\");\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3010, "output": 1040, "cacheRead": 14848, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 18898, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777941279399, "responseId": "resp_0785a90f67f31d840169f93b1fbfc881959ab993744e97f7bc"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_OCYxavohT5Vn3pvyslgCf9g1|fc_0785a90f67f31d840169f93b26e4cc8195ab5ef6504a384281", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1670 bytes to tests/src/org.mortbay.jetty/jetty-util/6.1.26/src/test/java/org_mortbay_jetty/jetty_util/LazyListTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777941289995}]}
